Check Brut Sightings From Data Base

check_raw_sightings.Rd

Checking the Sighting dataset extract directly from the Data base : colnames, missing values, etc. And it renames them in order to enter in the pelascope workflow.

Usage

check_raw_sightings(data_sighting)

Arguments

data_sighting

dataframe. Sighting table extract from the data base.

Value

Data sighting table clean and ready for the pelascope workflow.

Examples


data(data_sightings_brut)

check_raw_sightings(data_sightings_brut)
